                    already contain a provision described in paragraph
                    4;

as a deduction from the tax on the income of that resident, an amount equal
                    to the income tax paid in that other Contracting
                    Jurisdiction;

a company or other entity, if the principal class of its shares is
                    regularly traded on one or more recognised stock
                    exchanges;

